# One Clash rule per line. Blank lines and comments are ignored.
# Keep these rules under version control and edit them on your server.
#
# Examples:
# DOMAIN-SUFFIX,example.com,PROXY
# DOMAIN,api.example.org,DIRECT
#
# rules ended with "DIRECT" will be moved into dist/ruleset/custom-direct.yaml
# other rules will be moved into dist/ruleset/custom-proxy.yaml